Package com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.strings

Class FillerArrayStrings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.Filler<Array<T>>
      • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.FillerArray<java.lang.String>
        • com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.strings.FillerArrayStrings
  • public class FillerArrayStrings
extends FillerArray<java.lang.String>
    The class is the inheritor of the class FillerArray.

    This class fills an object of class Array with objects of String type, which is a wrapper over classical arrays.

    Created by Konstantin Lugowoy on 10.06.2018.

        public java.lang.String[] fill​(int lengthArray)
